      <title>津巴布韦将于本月就 210 亿美元债务问题举行会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/zimbabwe-ramps-up-talks-on-21-billion-debt-albatross-finance-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦将于本月晚些时候恢复与债权人的谈判，以重组 210 亿美元的外债，以摆脱自 1999 年以来导致其无法进入国际资本市场的债务违约问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/zimbabwe-ramps-up-talks-on-21-billion-debt-albatross-finance-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 14:27:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>托尔斯滕·斯洛克：明天对美联储来说很容易，12月则很难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-06/tomorrow-easy-for-fed-december-difficult-torsten-slok-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗管理公司首席经济学家托尔斯滕·斯洛克表示，市场需要“观望唐纳德·特朗普第二次担任总统后究竟会出台什么政策”，并研究利率走势和美联储未来面临的艰巨任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-06/tomorrow-easy-for-fed-december-difficult-torsten-slok-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 14:23:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长金多斯警告特朗普关税计划影响“巨大”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/ecb-s-guindos-warns-of-huge-implications-of-trump-tariff-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行副行长路易斯·德金多斯表示，如果美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普实施他在竞选期间威胁的进口关税，全球经济增长和通胀将面临潜在的不利冲击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/ecb-s-guindos-warns-of-huge-implications-of-trump-tariff-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 14:23:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>期货市场表明，比特币创纪录的涨势将获得动力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/futures-markets-suggest-record-breaking-bitcoin-rally-to-gain-momentum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[期货市场表明，唐纳德·特朗普在美国总统大选中获胜引发的比特币创纪录上涨可能才刚刚开始。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/futures-markets-suggest-record-breaking-bitcoin-rally-to-gain-momentum</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 14:23:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德准备成立 13 亿美元私人信贷延续基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/blackrock-readies-1-3-billion-private-credit-continuation-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，贝莱德公司正在设立一只私人信贷贷款基金，该基金将使其能够筹集最多 13 亿美元的资金并分配给现有投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/blackrock-readies-1-3-billion-private-credit-continuation-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 14:14:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选重燃通胀风险 债券价格创 2020 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/us-bonds-slide-most-since-pandemic-as-trump-renews-inflation-bet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债收益率飙升——30 年期国债收益率创下 2020 年 3 月全球套现浪潮以来的最大涨幅——因为投资者再次押注唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫将推高通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/us-bonds-slide-most-since-pandemic-as-trump-renews-inflation-bet</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 12:45:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普准备放松管制，高盛、花旗股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/goldman-citi-soar-on-hopes-of-less-tax-regulation-under-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者押注唐纳德·特朗普将兑现降低税收和减少银行业监管的承诺，花旗集团、摩根大通和高盛集团等美国银行的股价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/goldman-citi-soar-on-hopes-of-less-tax-regulation-under-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 11:56:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税风险冲击欧元、德国汽车股；可再生能源下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/european-stock-futures-drop-over-tariff-worries-as-trump-leads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普的选举胜利加剧了人们对征收进口关税的担忧，欧元创下了八年来最糟糕的一天，而汽车制造商等在美国拥有大量收入的行业表现不佳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/european-stock-futures-drop-over-tariff-worries-as-trump-leads</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 05:44:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的决定性胜利推高美元和收益率，黄金价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/gold-holds-steady-before-results-of-coin-toss-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普在选举中取得决定性胜利，结束了笼罩美国政坛的不确定性，导致黄金价格因债券收益率和美元走高而下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/gold-holds-steady-before-results-of-coin-toss-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:14:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选，标普 500 指数创历史新高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市创下历史新高，债券收益率飙升，美元出现自 2020 年 3 月以来的最大涨幅，投资者关注唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫以及他的政策对市场和经济的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:05:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
